  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randy dreams of becoming a great photographer. To help him, his grandfather lends him his camera, promising that he can keep it if he proves he’s ready.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a world full of challenges that you can overcome by using your camera in creative ways. Earn <strong>photographer badges</strong> by collecting film rolls in each level and show that you have what it takes to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But remember, the camera is just a tool, what truly matters is your creativity!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/11d3dc7d74544cbeca901e479dc062b1.poster.avif?t=1749630346\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/11d3dc7d74544cbeca901e479dc062b1.webm?t=1749630346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel across diverse thematic worlds, from lush green fields to a food world, and even outer space.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/eca824f0501899aef8bb1f81a6576bdc.poster.avif?t=1749630346\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/eca824f0501899aef8bb1f81a6576bdc.webm?t=1749630346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your camera to capture and move objects, eliminate them to reset their positions, and use your creativity to overcome challenges.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/b40b7f57da332624947bf934144a7ee7.poster.avif?t=1749630346\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/b40b7f57da332624947bf934144a7ee7.webm?t=1749630346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect as many film rolls as possible to earn badges and prove your photography skills.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/d7443be11f6966ee19c391a0395f4dd9.poster.avif?t=1749630346\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/d7443be11f6966ee19c391a0395f4dd9.webm?t=1749630346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and wear fun costumes while exploring the worlds. </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randy dreams of becoming a great photographer. To help him, his grandfather lends him his camera, promising that he can keep it if he proves he’s ready.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a world full of challenges that you can overcome by using your camera in creative ways. Earn <strong>photographer badges</strong> by collecting film rolls in each level and show that you have what it takes to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But remember, the camera is just a tool, what truly matters is your creativity!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/11d3dc7d74544cbeca901e479dc062b1.poster.avif?t=1749630346\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/11d3dc7d74544cbeca901e479dc062b1.webm?t=1749630346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel across diverse thematic worlds, from lush green fields to a food world, and even outer space.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/eca824f0501899aef8bb1f81a6576bdc.poster.avif?t=1749630346\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649930/extras/eca824f0501899aef8bb1f81a6576bdc.webm?t=1749630346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your camera to capture and move objects, eliminate them to reset their positions, and use your 